        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Adds the Control UI Projects workspace implementation: durable project store, Gateway project RPC methods, project/session association, resource notes/uploads, archive/restore, and the Projects dashboard tab.\n- Adds the SNES Studio dashboard surface and core SNES artifact builder used by the dashboard smoke path.\n- Adds a unified `pnpm ui:smoke:dashboard` suite for Projects, SNES Studio, and safe SNES hardware-proof artifact generation, then wires it into CI, release checks, and Full Release Validation rerun groups.\n- Documents the dashboard smoke commands, SNES Studio page, and release artifacts.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n- **Behavior or issue addressed:** Dashboard Projects and SNES Studio are implemented and covered by real Control UI smoke tests so CI/release can catch regressions in project persistence/archive/restore, SNES Studio browser create/edit/play/export, and safe SNES hardware-proof artifact generation.\n- **Real environment tested:** OpenClaw Mac Studio clean temp worktree at head `182e1e022bbd7212894c52075dd4374f68b69ab6`, Playwright Chromium against loopback `127.0.0.1`, local Dashboard Gateway-backed Projects smoke, static SNES Studio route smoke, and artifact output under `.artifacts/dashboard-smoke-suite/2026-05-31T01-19-17-216Z`.\n- **Exact steps or command run after this patch:** From the OpenClaw Mac Studio temp worktree, ran `pnpm ui:smoke:dashboard -- --artifact-profile local` against loopback Playwright Chromium after rebuilding and typechecking the rebased branch.\n- **Evidence after fix:** Dashboard smoke returned `\"ok\": true` with all three suite steps exit 0: Projects dashboard smoke, SNES Studio dashboard smoke, and SNES Studio hardware proof bundle. Projects smoke opened `http://127.0.0.1:64973/projects`, reported `authUrlClean: true`, created `Projects Smoke 1780190364426`, added a note resource, archived it through the dashboard UI, restored it through Archived Projects, and recorded no console, response, or page errors. SNES Studio smoke opened `http://127.0.0.1:65081/snes-studio?__openclaw_skip_auto_agent_team=1`, captured desktop/mobile screenshots, downloaded `.sfc`, emulator-proof JSON, and proof-run script artifacts, and verified the guided mobile flow.\n- **Observed result after fix:** Projects final store verified `total: 1`, `active: 1`, `archived: 0`; SNES Studio verified one-prompt Build With OpenClaw creation, 60 Hz runtime playtest canvas, selected-area prompt edits, preview/download flow, mobile guided flow, and explicit external-proof blockers for unavailable physical FXPAK/SRAM evidence while keeping the safe artifact bundle non-blocking.\n- **What was not tested:** Physical FXPAK PRO copy and post-power-cycle SRAM after-image evidence were not tested because no mounted FXPAK/SD2SNES-style volume or after-power-cycle SRAM image was available; the smoke records those as explicit non-blocking blockers unless `--require-complete` is used.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `pnpm tsgo:core && pnpm tsgo:test:src && pnpm tsgo:test:ui && pnpm tsgo:test:packages`\n- `pnpm test src/projects/store.test.ts src/gateway/server-methods/projects.test.ts ui/src/ui/controllers/projects.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/projects.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/snes-studio.test.ts packages/snes-studio-core/src/index.test.ts test/scripts/control-ui-dashboard-smoke-suite.test.ts test/scripts/snes-studio-hardware-proof.test.ts test/scripts/control-ui-snes-studio-smoke.test.ts test/scripts/control-ui-smoke-url.test.ts test/scripts/check-workflows.test.ts`\n- `pnpm build`\n- `pnpm check:docs`\n- `pnpm ui:smoke:dashboard -- --artifact-profile local`\n- `pnpm test test/scripts/check-workflows.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/check-workflows.mjs`\n- GitHub PR checks at head `182e1e022bbd7212894c52075dd4374f68b69ab6`: `Real behavior proof`, `Workflow Sanity / actionlint`, `Workflow Sanity / no-tabs`, `TUI PTY`, `Labeler`, `Auto response`, and `ClawSweeper Dispatch` passed; PR is mergeable and remains